	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2014-04-27T22:52:02">Xeros Technology Group PLC is a holding company. The Company, through its subsidiaries, is engaged in the research, development and commercialization of polymer bead cleaning alternatives to traditional aqueous based cleaning. The Companys polymer bead cleaning system reduces the carbon footprint of the entire laundry process. In addition to the commercial laundry market, the Companys polymer bead technology has a range of applications in other industries, including domestic laundry, leather processing, garment finishing, and metal cleaning. The Company is in various stages of development and preparation for commercialization of other identified applications. The Company has two wholly owned subsidiaries: Xeros Limited and Xeros Inc.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2015-12-02T12:28:57">BRIEF: For the fiscal year ended 31 July 2015, Xeros Technology Group PLC revenues increased 49% to L466K. Net loss increased 60% to L10.2M. Revenues reflect North America segment increase of 47% to L378K, Europe segment increase of 60% to L88K. Higher net loss reflects Staff Costs, Recruitment &amp; Other HR in A increase of 71% to L4.6M (expense), Administrative Expenses Balancing Value increase of 73% to L3.2M (expense).</Text>
	</TextInfo>
